diff --git a/gcc/ChangeLog b/gcc/ChangeLog
index f01e9376214..23bc70cb93f 100644
--- a/gcc/ChangeLog
+++ b/gcc/ChangeLog
@@ -1,3 +1,32 @@
+2026-04-23  Bjorkus "ThePhD" Dorkus  <phdofthehouse@gmail.com>
+
+	* doc/extend.texi: document new __builtin_std_embed builtin.
+	List potential extension points.
+	* builtins.cc (fold_builtin_std_embed): new function for initiating
+	potential constant folding of a __builtin_std_embed call.
+	* c-common.cc (check_builtin_std_embed): new function for type checking
+	new __builtin_std_embed function.
+	* builtins.cc (fold_builtin_varargs): new _BUILT_IN_STD_EMBED case to
+	call newly added function for folding __builtin_std_embed.
+	* builtins.def: add new BUILT_IN_STD_EMBED/"std_embed" GCC builtin.
+	Synchronized with clang implementation.
+	* builtin-types.def: new variable type and 2 new reference types.
+	* incpath.h: new INC_DEPEND header chain, new function declarations
+	for cpp_dep_pattern type and cpp_dep_* helper functions.
+	* incpath.cc: one new include for regex, new cpp_dep_pattern forward
+	type. cpp_dep_pattern* usability function implementations. Helper
+	function append_file_to_dir_name, basic finding functions.
+	deps_head and deps_tail for storage of input dependencies from #depend
+	directive.
+	search_path_kind, search_path_with_dir.
+	* tree-core.h: new type global_constant_evaluation_link. New constant
+	evaluation stack tracking functions and accessors for global variable
+	that is a forward-linked list.
+	* tree.cc: implementation of new global_constant_evaluation_link
+	functions.
+	* tree.h (strip_pointer_types_by): new inline helper function for partial
+	pointer type stripping.
+
 2026-04-22  Sam James  <sam@gentoo.org>
 
 	* ipa-prop.cc (param_type_may_change_p): Fix comment typo.
